title: EP 89: A Do-What?!
itunes:title: EP 89: A Do-What?!
description:
It’s Thursday! This week AJ and TamBam touch on a few hot topics, mainly Nia Long’s Big man letting his “little man” ruin his life. Secondly, Rihanna Bowl 2023 is in full effect, y’all going!? For the main topic Susan “The Birth Doula” Spells joins your host to discuss black women and pregnancy and how black women are over 3x more likely to die during pregnancy and postpartum than our white counterparts. Is at home birth the best option for us at this point?  Tune in!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
